---
import Layout from "../../layouts/LayoutProject.astro";
---

<Layout title="Venus.com">
  <p>One of my first projects in Moovweb</p>
  <h2>Project goals</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Develop mobile version of existing site</li>
    <li>Integrate analytics</li>
    <li>Speed up the mobile site as much as possible</li>
    <li>Add automatically generated interactive AMP version of pages</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>My Participation</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Team Lead</li>
    <li>Client communication</li>
    <li>Co-piloting PM's</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>Achievments</h2>
  <!-- p>We released with 3 months delay the project and achieved:</p -->

  <figure>
    <img
      src="/img/projects/venus-com.png"
      alt="Venus.com PLP to PDP transition"
    />
    <figcaption>
      Improve <dfn title="Product List Page">PLP</dfn> to <dfn
        title="Product Details Page">PDP</dfn
      > transition to 0.5&thinsp;sec.
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-1of2">
      <h3>Speed</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          500ms median page loads <dfn title="Largest Contentful Paint "
            >(LCP)</dfn
          >
        </li>
        <li>300ms average AMP page loads from search</li>
        <li>
          70.5% users increase in first load speeds dropping from 3.4 seconds to
          1 second
        </li>
        <li>
          <dfn
            title="It means we cache everything except user-related data of the site"
            >80%+ cache hit rate</dfn
          > for dynamic content at the edge
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-1of2">
      <h3>Sales</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>30% lift in organic conversion rate</li>
        <li>30% lift in overall revenue with a sub-second website</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
